data.description: Introducing a charming bi-level home located in an area with many mature trees. This spacious residence offers over 2200 finished square feet of living space. With its 4-5 bedrooms and 1.5 bathrooms, this home is perfect for those seeking both comfort and room to grow. Hardwood flooring throughout the main level. The open-concept design seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, providing a perfect space for both everyday living and entertaining. The main level also features four bedrooms, offering ample space for family, guests, or the flexibility to create a home office or hobby room. Downstairs, the lower level is a true gem, featuring two generously sized rooms. There is a 24 x 14 family room, which is currently used as a Master Bedroom and a 20 x 15 rec/game room, perfect for entertainment or recreation. A 15 x 9 bar area and half bathroom complete this lower level. The 26 x 24 two-car garage provides ample room for your vehicles and additional storage needs. Don't miss this opportunity for a comfortable and versatile living space.
